snippet.title: F1® Manager 24 | Feature Focus - Create A Team. Create A Legacy.
snippet.description:
Learn more about the new Create A Team mode coming to F1® Manager 24 with the first of our Feature Focus deep dives. Learn more: https://www.f1manager.com/features/new/create-a-team-create-a-legacy

F1® Manager 24 releases on PC and consoles, July 23rd 2024. Pre-order Now: https://fron.dev/YT-F1M24-PO
